headline: Best Stock to Buy Right Now: Uber vs. DoorDash
summary: In the U.S., Uber Technologies (NYSE: UBER) and DoorDash (NASDAQ: DASH) dominate the food delivery business.  Of the two, DoorDash claims the most market share in online food delivery, placing it far ahead of Uber Eats and likely leading some investors to assume that it could be an obvious choice between the two.

headline: Uber and OpenTable team up to enhance dining experience
summary: The collaboration combines Uber's ride-hailing and delivery with OpenTable's networks in Australia, Canada, Ireland, Mexico, the UK and the US.
